<item>
            <title>[LU-8144] add lazyinit progress support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8144</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Somtimes, we need figure out progress of Lazyinit for OST ldiskfs.&lt;br/&gt;
We might need add stats support that is useful to debug and watch how far lazyinit has gone.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
